{"tid":2134226,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男子虛報羈留期間被警員毆打 下月3日西九龍裁判法院提堂","createTime":"2020-07-31T14:15:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T03:01:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4ae315efc5550608fa32d442aa530f9002eb9feb","tid":2134226,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:15:46.000Z","msg":"一名46歲姓梁男子上月28日，在旺角區因涉嫌「店舖盜竊」被警拘捕，之後被帶往旺角警署扣留調查。男子被捕翌日，警方落案起訴男子一項「店舖盜竊」罪。男子於被起訴當日作出投訴，指自己在扣留期間，在旺角警署羈留室被一名警務人員毆打。<br />\n<br />\n案件轉交投訴警察課跟進，經深入調查及徵詢律政司意見後，警方在昨日(30日)拘捕該名男子，並以「虛報有人犯罪」落案起訴男子。案件將於下月3日於西九龍裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\nSource: 東網"},{"pid":"a092377f9a2aebc6cee0e54d2c0318e3950b6eac","tid":2134226,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:16:57.000Z","msg":"原告變被告<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d8f4e52bca41e0eb6d3f5adc1ec1803bf81656","tid":2134226,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a092377f9a2aebc6cee0e54d2c0318e3950b6eac","tid":2134226,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:16:57.000Z","msg":"原告變被告<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:17:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"403f4d7244492b57d3572b6a7e5575d20c8f2b6c","tid":2134226,"uid":88743,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:18:18.000Z","msg":"今日有單警二代俾警察打一巴就俾人告到坐監"},{"pid":"dbb62987e5cd4cd61050905b8db96975b05e2a6a","tid":2134226,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"403f4d7244492b57d3572b6a7e5575d20c8f2b6c","tid":2134226,"uid":88743,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:18:18.000Z","msg":"今日有單警二代俾警察打一巴就俾人告到坐監"},"